<br>
Having our familars present should give wizards an increased chance of scoring a critical blast. Wizards now have an inherent chance score a critical blast, and will AA points we can increase the chances as well. This is a nice way of increasing our damage output and providing more help to the group without adding a new line of spells for wizard.<br>
<br>
adds another 2% for Minor Familar (29th level)<br>
